data.meta_description: This upbeat and empowering original song by composer Garrett Breeze is a synth pop-infused statement of confidence and joy full of catchy hooks and fun vocal moments. It was commissioned and premiered by the combined 7th and 8th grade choir of Sioux Center Middle School in Iowa.  Performance / learning tracks available HERE.  Optional rhythm section accompaniment parts available HERE. data.text:
This upbeat and empowering original song by composer Garrett Breeze is a synth pop-infused statement of confidence and joy full of catchy hooks and fun vocal moments. It was commissioned and premiered by the combined 7th and 8th grade choir of Sioux Center Middle School in Iowa. Performance / learning tracks available HERE. Optional rhythm section accompaniment parts available HERE.

Difficulty: Easy Intermediate

Voicing: SATB, SAB, SSA, TTB, and Two-Part

Accompaniment: Piano, Rhythm Section, or Performance Track
